feedback_history.text:
-= Shed =-
You've walked into a standard room. Your mind races to think of what kind of room would be standard. And then it hits you. Of course. You're in the shed.

You see an opened toolbox. What a letdown! The toolbox is empty! You see a gleam over in a corner, where you can see a workbench. But the thing is empty, unfortunately.

There is an open barn door leading north.
